{"id": "1406333181145251941", "channel_id": "1406285155013886044", "type": 0, "author_id": "302004389927845889", "author_name": "darkfeet", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330303307579492/image.png?ex=68a212a8&is=68a0c128&hm=863b06d40dd34a63b5a90fa6f4b3586cf2433f8b30f049050c059605a89da4c3&\nhttps://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330304091656342/image.png?ex=68a212a8&is=68a0c128&hm=2fe3cbc9e6cac0f1c05f8529d9df16aa4b9835ce302209a937fce9159da7e8b0&\nhttps://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330607465660650/image.png?ex=68a212f1&is=68a0c171&hm=9c3c781d12b9b72b79feb29cff8d5c25ead796851a749260a10045e179ebeaa9&\nhttps://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330608548053002/image.png?ex=68a212f1&is=68a0c171&hm=a9f8f1cda4012e97239030117051dba39b2f78e2db03788e908921badc3f5a69&\n\nI'm not sure if its intentional or not, but im quite sure i've seen it work before.\n\nTawil's 2d Enlightenment grants all chosen cards from Exalt Prepare 1, so in combination with certain cards already having Prepare, it results into Prepare 2 as expected. Although lately i have been encountering the situations where it still functions as Prepare 1 (At the same time tooltip always states Prepare 2), besides i definitely remember picking Lightning Retribution on Tawil and it reducing it's cost by 2 at the end of turn, without any discard mechanics being involved \n\nIn the following attached screenshots it can be seen that the tooltip states: \"Prepare 2\", despite that the cost is only reduced by 1 (Only 1 card was cast between 1st and 2d pair of screenshots: six wings to transition the boss to the next phase)", "timestamp": "2025-08-16T17:45:58.792000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-17T16:22:45.404000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "image", "title": "", "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330303307579492/image.png?ex=68a212a8&is=68a0c128&hm=863b06d40dd34a63b5a90fa6f4b3586cf2433f8b30f049050c059605a89da4c3&", "description": ""}, {"type": "image", "title": "", "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330304091656342/image.png?ex=68a212a8&is=68a0c128&hm=2fe3cbc9e6cac0f1c05f8529d9df16aa4b9835ce302209a937fce9159da7e8b0&", "description": ""}, {"type": "image", "title": "", "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330607465660650/image.png?ex=68a212f1&is=68a0c171&hm=9c3c781d12b9b72b79feb29cff8d5c25ead796851a749260a10045e179ebeaa9&", "description": ""}, {"type": "image", "title": "", "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1363906093008293931/1406330608548053002/image.png?ex=68a212f1&is=68a0c171&hm=a9f8f1cda4012e97239030117051dba39b2f78e2db03788e908921badc3f5a69&", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1406285155013886044", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Tawil, Inconsistent 1 Arithemetica discount application on Omniscient Verity (Skill 1)", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
